snippet.textDisplay:
I have seen this hundreds of times, as part of my daily meditative practice. But realized - None of the musicians are looking at notes / sheet music?!?! What the heck?  This is such an intricate and difficult qawwali. Have they memorized the entire (10+ minutes) of musical lines, or, just naturally gifted , or both ?! 
Goes to show how talented all the musicians and singers are in this awesome production ... including of course Atif -- who blows the roof off with his beautiful, powerful voice and soft touches.  
Madeene chalain ... Let's go! This month! Why wait.
